#N canvas 0 0 900 480 12;
#X text 20 16 state-table.pd -- per-state scene parameters\, indexed by shrine-state (0 quiet .. 4 ascending).;
#X text 20 34 Fills four arrays at load. A scene consumer reads one column with [tabread <name>] at the shrine-state index.;
#X text 20 52 PROVISIONAL + SEAM ONLY: columns chosen for the texture engine (texture-test.pd). Nothing consumes these yet.;
#X text 20 88 scene-gain   0-1 master level    : 0.10 0.30 0.50 0.75 1.00;
#X text 20 106 scene-voices count active 0-3   : 0 1 2 3 3;
#X text 20 124 scene-wet    0-1 reverb/chorus   : 0.20 0.30 0.45 0.60 0.85;
#X text 20 142 scene-rate   0-1 note density    : 0.20 0.35 0.50 0.70 1.00;
#X obj 30 190 loadbang;
#X msg 30 230 \; scene-gain 0 0.1 0.3 0.5 0.75 1 \; scene-voices 0 0 1 2 3 3 \; scene-wet 0 0.2 0.3 0.45 0.6 0.85 \; scene-rate 0 0.2 0.35 0.5 0.7 1;
#X obj 30 300 table scene-gain 5;
#X obj 30 330 table scene-voices 5;
#X obj 30 360 table scene-wet 5;
#X obj 30 390 table scene-rate 5;
#X connect 7 0 8 0;
